Package: shutdown-kvm-guest
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libvirt-bin
Recommends: qemu-kvm
Description: Script to assist in cleanly shutting down KVM guests
 This is a simple initscript that shuts down kvm VMs with a 'virsh
 shutdown <domain>', which makes them exit cleanly.
